{"id": 2404, "genre": 1001, "title": "社交网络上你都有哪些微妙的朋友类型？", "description": "我最多的是，虽然觉得可能会有需要但加了不多久就受不了选择“不看ta朋友圈”型朋友。你呢？（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 2268, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180608101901qcvjfOZTKXIhlMu3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 286209, "content": "没事不找我   找我必有事   ", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316543}, {"id": 286210, "content": "无论如何热烈的聊天，都不会觉得是朋友！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036408}, {"id": 286723, "content": "想要交流但不知从何说起，于是……只点赞朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366686}, {"id": 286212, "content": "微信只是新时代通信录而已，有误解的可能是你自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951328}, {"id": 286468, "content": "知乎已成为最大同志交友软件，了解一下?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327849}, {"id": 286469, "content": "全是做微商的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371098}, {"id": 289541, "content": "加了好友 因为不是很熟又怕打扰到他 其实很想找他聊天 微信页面点了无数次又删 结果到现在就聊过一次 再也没响起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385441}, {"id": 286214, "content": "就是想说点什么但却不能说些什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367725}, {"id": 286470, "content": "聊不到三句要微信号，从此以后除了职业咨询再无下文…微商基本屏蔽＋删除。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591076}, {"id": 286215, "content": "为什么有的人加了好友却一句话都没聊过的", "image": "img/option/option/20180608130711d3t7K95iIyQp4fne", "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658495}, {"id": 286216, "content": "整天瞎扯，大网骗，从不说真实的个人信息，却聊的很开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360864}, {"id": 286217, "content": "有相同兴趣但不怎么联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172833}, {"id": 286218, "content": "为啥最近好奇心老关心我的朋友？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 286219, "content": "微信上的应用型好友，如修电器的，理发的，美甲的，需要时才去联络", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780604}, {"id": 286476, "content": "出去玩什么的从来不找你，有事了，才会想起你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371133}, {"id": 286222, "content": "在以前加的小学同学，到现在也只有几个略有联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367697}, {"id": 286991, "content": "从来不聊天只活在自己动态里，联系仅限于点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373063}, {"id": 286224, "content": "八面玲珑，一面一好友，偏偏可以触及内心的人又不曾谋面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956601}, {"id": 286226, "content": "只能是网友型朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929606}, {"id": 286230, "content": "因工作而加的不知道有生之年还用不用得上的“好友”", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660957}, {"id": 286742, "content": "找你借了钱后，都没了，只能靠唠嗑，其他的还是免了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372057}, {"id": 286233, "content": "给我的每一条发言点赞，却从来不和我说话。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213263}, {"id": 286234, "content": "她在国外读书，半年聊一次天，友谊依旧❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20180608161454Qx9kBJCnlbN0FtT4.jpg", "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368564}, {"id": 286235, "content": "天之道，损有余而补不足。", "image": "img/option/option/20180608163144HqhEslN1vQFWuSro", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368581}, {"id": 293404, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407146}, {"id": 286493, "content": "屏蔽他但会偷偷点开朋友圈的好友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371221}, {"id": 288798, "content": "估计就是加了微信，就没聊过一句，要不然就是尬聊状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 286239, "content": "没事不找我，打电话给我一定有事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1252241}, {"id": 286240, "content": "平时不说话结婚生子发邀请", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735416}, {"id": 287011, "content": "加了什么英文字啊情话墙啊网易云热评君啊之类的Q友，看他们发的一些有意思的句子，时不时偷一个发说说，哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373161}, {"id": 286244, "content": "没有朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368660}, {"id": 287529, "content": "可能很久不见很久不你聊，但一旦某天聊起来，又会没完没了，没有固定的话题，没有特定的时间，基本也不会秒回", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375581}, {"id": 286259, "content": "我个人平常不喜欢聊天，社交网络大多数作为一种应用工具，如贴吧、知乎等只在需要找资料或了解一些知识时使用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368679}, {"id": 286262, "content": "有些网络上的朋友，比现实中的朋友靠谱多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366879}, {"id": 286263, "content": "没有朋友，只有工作和广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368709}, {"id": 286264, "content": "Alohaed each other, but never talked.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883487}, {"id": 286265, "content": "没追到的姑娘吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368718}, {"id": 286266, "content": "我是来试验的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368719}, {"id": 286270, "content": "就那种网上聊的特欢‘但一当面聊天就经常无话可说的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368748}, {"id": 286271, "content": "以前玩的很好，分开了之后想要发信息不知道怎么编辑的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368782}, {"id": 286272, "content": "路人型伪朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722823}, {"id": 286276, "content": "曾经为了朋友圈多刷漂亮照片，现在的朋友圈只是我用来保留美好回忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368819}, {"id": 286277, "content": "一句“在吗？”都让我觉得害怕?", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359873}, {"id": 286278, "content": "家人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368823}, {"id": 286279, "content": "SB", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905876}, {"id": 286281, "content": "默默看她们的朋友圈并且羡慕“真人赢啊”\n然后匆匆挤上地铁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327609}, {"id": 286283, "content": "明明都不是很熟悉了，突然过来借钱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323392}, {"id": 286284, "content": "我加了一个好友，是在网易云上相约一起去看一场livehouse认识的。但自那之后，我们再也没说过话，发朋友圈分享音乐都会互相点赞或者在评论聊几句，双方似乎都很有默契地仅限于此，即使知道趣味相投，可还是不愿破坏这微妙的情谊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196762}, {"id": 286286, "content": "无事献殷勤 非奸即盗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368892}, {"id": 286287, "content": "我的研友。每天彼此鼓励、打卡、分享观点，是我的动力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342805}]}